1
00:01:32,410 --> 00:01:39,950
[Better Halves]

2
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:43,009
[Episode 11]

3
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,190
Chief Lu has offered 10,000 taels

4
00:02:13,190 --> 00:02:14,530
to Marriage Broker Shi.

5
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,300
Marriage Broker Shi wins.

6
00:02:20,420 --> 00:02:21,870
Great!

7
00:02:21,890 --> 00:02:22,670
Great!

8
00:02:25,510 --> 00:02:29,829
[Heaven Rewards the Diligent]

9
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,400
Since the results are in,

10
00:02:27,740 --> 00:02:30,070
Miss Shi, please go back and prepare well.

11
00:02:30,550 --> 00:02:32,350
Don't disappoint the sponsors.

12
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,000
So Brother Lu did this

13
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:42,960
to help me.

14
00:02:52,900 --> 00:02:55,340
[No.1 Matchmaker in the World]

15
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:57,079
Mother, I'm back.

16
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,050
How did it go?

17
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:01,680
Ke, you must be exhausted today.

18
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:02,520
I'm not tired.

19
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:04,540
Mother, I won!

20
00:03:06,220 --> 00:03:08,820
Our family can host
the Flower Assembly again!

21
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:11,730
This year, I'll help you run
the Flower Assembly.

22
00:03:11,830 --> 00:03:13,670
Mother, I did it!

23
00:03:13,830 --> 00:03:15,300
My good daughter,

24
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,970
thank you, my child.

25
00:03:16,990 --> 00:03:18,450
I truly thank you.

26
00:03:18,590 --> 00:03:19,870
Don't mention it, Mother.

27
00:03:19,870 --> 00:03:21,140
As long as you're happy.

28
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:23,630
I am happy, very happy!

29
00:03:23,770 --> 00:03:24,710
Cousin, you're amazing!

30
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:26,110
You've brought honor to the family!

31
00:03:26,110 --> 00:03:27,010
My daughter is the best.

32
00:03:27,010 --> 00:03:27,810
The very best!

33
00:03:28,990 --> 00:03:30,190
My sister is the best!

34
00:03:30,990 --> 00:03:32,170
Thank you, Brother.

35
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:50,150
I wonder if Brother Lu is home.

36
00:03:56,770 --> 00:03:58,170
Whether he's home or not,

37
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,840
I'll give it a try.

38
00:04:29,610 --> 00:04:31,070
Why isn't there any sound?

39
00:04:50,890 --> 00:04:54,040
Never mind. It's fine if he's not here.

40
00:04:55,830 --> 00:04:57,440
Some things are hard to say

41
00:04:58,780 --> 00:04:59,840
face-to-face.

42
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:05,460
Brother Lu, thank you.

43
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:09,950
I can't repay you
for everything you've done for me.

44
00:05:12,140 --> 00:05:13,470
Besides saying thanks,

45
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:16,480
I also need to apologize to you.

46
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:18,230
You were trying to help me,

47
00:05:18,230 --> 00:05:20,560
but I didn't understand your intentions.

48
00:05:21,790 --> 00:05:22,700
Brother Lu,

49
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:25,350
when I said I never wanted
to see you again,

50
00:05:25,350 --> 00:05:27,060
I didn't mean it.

51
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:29,490
I just didn't know how to face you.

52
00:05:30,380 --> 00:05:33,900
My marriage was arranged from childhood.

53
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:37,570
But that person never showed up
to fulfil the agreement.

54
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,580
I don't know what to do.

55
00:05:42,170 --> 00:05:44,230
It seems that person isn't He Kexian.

56
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,380
He hasn't shown up yet.

57
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:55,630
Tomorrow, I'll start preparing for
the Flower Assembly.

58
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:58,900
I should go now.

59
00:06:06,380 --> 00:06:07,080
Ke.

60
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:09,710
Since you think I'm a good person,

61
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,790
could you give me a chance

62
00:06:12,890 --> 00:06:14,290
to love you for life?

63
00:06:24,110 --> 00:06:24,990
Idiots.

64
00:06:25,190 --> 00:06:26,480
All the assassins I sent

65
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:28,590
were taken out by Lu Chi.

66
00:06:28,830 --> 00:06:31,540
And now the Flower Assembly
was lost to Shi Fa'ke.

67
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:33,520
I think all my men are like you.

68
00:06:33,630 --> 00:06:35,230
They're all fools. Donkeys!

69
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:38,050
My Lord, it was that Marriage Broker Deng
who didn't do her job.

70
00:06:38,050 --> 00:06:40,450
Not only did we get no silver
from the Flower Assembly,

71
00:06:40,450 --> 00:06:42,250
we even lost the hosting rights.

72
00:06:42,330 --> 00:06:43,710
What should we do?

73
00:06:45,340 --> 00:06:46,830
Since this Shi Fa'ke

74
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:49,230
loves hosting the Flower Assembly so much,

75
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:51,820
I'll make it a real spectacle for her.

76
00:06:52,210 --> 00:06:57,540
[A Perfect Match]

77
00:06:53,780 --> 00:06:54,360
My Lord!

78
00:06:54,380 --> 00:06:55,510
Marriage Broker Deng.

79
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:58,710
You even lost the hosting rights
for the Flower Assembly.

80
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,160
My Lord, I was wrong.

81
00:07:01,380 --> 00:07:03,080
You couldn't even handle

82
00:07:03,100 --> 00:07:04,510
someone as insignificant as Shi Fa'ke.

83
00:07:04,510 --> 00:07:05,240
I think

84
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:07,650
you should vacate your position
as Chief Matchmaker as soon as possible.

85
00:07:07,650 --> 00:07:08,980
Let someone more capable take over!

86
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:11,370
[A Perfect Match]

87
00:07:09,710 --> 00:07:11,730
My Lord, please don't do this.

88
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:12,560
You know

89
00:07:12,580 --> 00:07:14,930
I've dedicated my entire life to
becoming Chief Matchmaker.

90
00:07:14,930 --> 00:07:16,220
My Lord, please don't!

91
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:16,810
Let go!

92
00:07:22,030 --> 00:07:23,020
My Lord!

93
00:07:23,770 --> 00:07:28,450
[A Perfect Match]

94
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:34,150
[Xibao Pavilion]

95
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:44,010
[Xibao Pavilion]

96
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:48,880
Pan'er, I'm here to deliver VIP tickets

97
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:49,520
and also...

98
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:50,350
Miss Shi,

99
00:07:50,690 --> 00:07:53,290
at Xibao Pavilion,
he's the one who makes decisions.

100
00:07:53,290 --> 00:07:55,730
Please speak with him.

101
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,960
Brother Lu.

102
00:08:07,130 --> 00:08:09,190
I'm here to deliver the VIP tickets.

103
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,130
[Flower Assembly]

104
00:08:09,870 --> 00:08:12,980
Too many people
signed up for the assembly.

105
00:08:13,310 --> 00:08:14,690
Only those with tickets

106
00:08:14,710 --> 00:08:17,370
will be allowed on stage
to talk with the ladies.

107
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:19,220
Having everyone come
to Xibao Pavilion for tickets

108
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:19,100
[Flower Assembly]

109
00:08:19,380 --> 00:08:21,890
will also boost Xibao Pavilion's business.

110
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,480
Okay.

111
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,240
I'll tell Ms. Li

112
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:27,020
to take good care of everyone.

113
00:08:27,540 --> 00:08:28,940
Today, I'll send someone

114
00:08:29,110 --> 00:08:32,309
to deliver the money
to the Official Matchmaking Agency.

115
00:08:32,730 --> 00:08:34,770
That much silver in the agency

116
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,260
might attract thieves.

117
00:08:36,490 --> 00:08:38,419
If Xibao Pavilion has inventory,

118
00:08:38,570 --> 00:08:40,169
we can help clear your stock.

119
00:08:40,169 --> 00:08:41,250
If not,

120
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:43,570
the marriage brokers can make purchases,

121
00:08:43,570 --> 00:08:45,160
and then settle accounts with you later.

122
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,290
How does that sound?

123
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:49,820
As expected, you always think ahead.

124
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:54,750
Then I'll trouble you to
come to the agency for a few days.

125
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:58,680
It's no trouble.

126
00:08:59,490 --> 00:09:00,300
Let's go then.

127
00:09:00,330 --> 00:09:00,860
Let's go.

128
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:08,240
What?

129
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:11,610
Shi Fa'ke may be hosting
the Flower Assembly,

130
00:09:11,610 --> 00:09:13,200
but I am the Chief Matchmaker.

131
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,130
All the accounts

132
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:16,100
should go through me!

133
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:17,500
Regarding the accounts,

134
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:19,470
there's no need to trouble you,
Chief Matchmaker Deng.

135
00:09:19,470 --> 00:09:21,170
This time, all expenses
will be reimbursed as reported.

136
00:09:21,170 --> 00:09:22,290
Xibao Pavilion will check all purchases

137
00:09:22,290 --> 00:09:24,040
against market prices,

138
00:09:24,070 --> 00:09:25,020
count the items,

139
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:27,990
and verify them
against the receipts before payment.

140
00:09:27,990 --> 00:09:29,890
That way, we prevent corruption

141
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,240
and save manpower.

142
00:09:33,170 --> 00:09:34,940
Shi Fa'ke, youâ€”

143
00:09:34,970 --> 00:09:36,160
Chief Matchmaker Deng,

144
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:38,000
you're unfamiliar

145
00:09:38,020 --> 00:09:39,310
with the accounts of the Flower Assembly,

146
00:09:39,310 --> 00:09:40,730
so there's no need to trouble yourself.

147
00:09:40,730 --> 00:09:41,660
What did you say?

148
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,180
Colleagues,

149
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:54,080
if you've purchased any items,

150
00:09:54,110 --> 00:09:55,560
please present your receipts.

151
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:56,780
Once we've verified everything,

152
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:59,380
we can go to Xibao Pavilion
to collect payment.

153
00:10:01,370 --> 00:10:04,210
Thank you all for your hard work
for the Flower Assembly,

154
00:10:04,210 --> 00:10:06,060
I will certainly make it worth your while.

155
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:08,510
Everyone who goes to Xibao Pavilion
to collect payment

156
00:10:08,510 --> 00:10:10,080
will receive complimentary tea.

157
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:12,140
Thank you, Chief Lu.

158
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:16,790
Here.

159
00:10:29,430 --> 00:10:31,340
[Receipt]

160
00:10:38,530 --> 00:10:41,150
[Receipt]

161
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,750
Crispy, delicious, and not too greasy.

162
00:10:50,050 --> 00:10:52,250
He's Bakery really lives up to its name.

163
00:10:54,410 --> 00:10:55,810
He's complimenting you.

164
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:58,210
I'm glad you like it, Ke.

165
00:10:59,420 --> 00:11:00,210
Ketian,

166
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:02,730
Brother Lu has already stamped this.

167
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:02,640
[Receipt]

168
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:06,420
You can go to Xibao Pavilion to collect
the money when you're free.

169
00:11:06,950 --> 00:11:08,000
So much money?

170
00:11:09,010 --> 00:11:10,710
This is what He's Bakery deserves.

171
00:11:10,710 --> 00:11:13,370
I can't let you contribute
both labor and money.

172
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:15,010
Chief Lu is truly generous.

173
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:30,900
[Novel Shop]

174
00:11:37,020 --> 00:11:38,950
Young Master, what book
are you looking for?

175
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:39,180
[Lu Zhuxi, Mount Qianya]

176
00:11:39,510 --> 00:11:41,430
We have The Analects, the Four Books,

177
00:11:41,430 --> 00:11:42,670
Comprehensive Examination of
Figures Past and Present,

178
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:43,600
we have them all.

179
00:11:43,970 --> 00:11:44,570
Boss.

180
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:47,420
What's your best-selling novel?

181
00:11:47,450 --> 00:11:48,840
For novels,

182
00:11:48,860 --> 00:11:51,190
the ones by Neighboring Hermit
are the most popular.

183
00:11:51,190 --> 00:11:52,760
However, for the past month,

184
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,620
he hasn't released any new chapters.

185
00:11:54,620 --> 00:11:56,820
The readers are desperate.

186
00:11:56,850 --> 00:11:58,380
My business is affected too.

187
00:11:58,380 --> 00:11:59,910
I've lost quite a bit of income.

188
00:11:59,910 --> 00:12:01,480
It's hard. Truly hard.

189
00:12:01,620 --> 00:12:02,490
I suffer,

190
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,660
and so do the people.

191
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,770
Here's another one

192
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,280
who's gone mad waiting for
Neighboring Hermit's novels.

193
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:11,470
Boss, any new volumes yet?

194
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:15,630
Miss Zhu, you came in person?

195
00:12:15,660 --> 00:12:16,910
Whatever novels you like,

196
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:17,890
just write a list and send it over.

197
00:12:17,890 --> 00:12:19,510
I can deliver them to your home myself.

198
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:20,350
Boss,

199
00:12:20,390 --> 00:12:21,490
I haven't read

200
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:23,310
Neighboring Hermit's novels in a while.

201
00:12:23,310 --> 00:12:24,740
I've read some others,

202
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:27,620
but I only want
Neighboring Hermit's new chapters.

203
00:12:27,690 --> 00:12:28,820
Neighboring Hermit

204
00:12:28,850 --> 00:12:31,160
hasn't written a single word for a month.

205
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,860
Why don't you take a look at this one?

206
00:12:32,860 --> 00:12:34,380
It's by Nine-Turn Scholar

207
00:12:34,410 --> 00:12:35,190
and it's quite good too.

208
00:12:35,190 --> 00:12:36,390
That won't be necessary.

209
00:12:36,390 --> 00:12:38,350
I only read Neighboring Hermit.

210
00:12:38,660 --> 00:12:40,390
Boss, if a new chapter arrives,

211
00:12:40,410 --> 00:12:42,010
please deliver it to my home.

212
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:43,440
Rest assured,

213
00:12:43,450 --> 00:12:44,540
if a new chapter comes,

214
00:12:44,540 --> 00:12:46,660
I'll deliver them
to the Prime Minister's residence.

215
00:12:46,660 --> 00:12:47,190
Let's go.

216
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:49,330
Take care.

217
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:54,500
Who knew this young lady was so pretty

218
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:56,350
and had such great taste?

219
00:12:59,270 --> 00:13:00,910
This is an authentic piece.

220
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:01,600
Really?

221
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,660
It must be quite valuable.

222
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,870
Look at these color combinations.

223
00:13:07,870 --> 00:13:09,530
They're absolutely perfect.

224
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:11,790
I don't think I saw this
when I was here last time.

225
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:13,270
These must be updated daily.

226
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:14,630
Whenever something sells,

227
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:16,290
they put new items on display.

228
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:23,280
Young Master,

229
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:25,980
Would you like to take a look at
our new arrivals?

230
00:13:25,980 --> 00:13:28,610
For family, we have pearls,
jade, and glass lamps.

231
00:13:28,610 --> 00:13:31,800
For the ladies, we have necklaces,
earrings, and hairpins.

232
00:13:31,800 --> 00:13:33,570
We have it all.

233
00:13:34,690 --> 00:13:35,890
Your chiefâ€”

234
00:13:35,990 --> 00:13:37,020
What bad timing,

235
00:13:37,300 --> 00:13:38,500
our chief isn't here.

236
00:13:38,850 --> 00:13:40,740
If you have urgent business,

237
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:42,380
feel free to leave your name.

238
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,740
Not here? That's good.

239
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:47,090
Ms. Li, go about your business.

240
00:13:47,220 --> 00:13:48,480
Bring me some fine tea.

241
00:13:48,650 --> 00:13:50,610
I want that... Snow-Tipped Jade!

242
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:58,090
He knows who our chief is
and isn't afraid of him.

243
00:13:59,060 --> 00:14:00,930
He knows my full name,

244
00:14:01,770 --> 00:14:03,590
yet I don't know his face.

245
00:14:04,500 --> 00:14:07,590
The Snow-Tipped Jade
only arrived three days ago.

246
00:14:08,330 --> 00:14:10,060
In the capital, besides me

247
00:14:10,260 --> 00:14:11,450
and Chief,

248
00:14:11,680 --> 00:14:13,540
even Lu Yi might not know about it.

249
00:14:14,830 --> 00:14:17,810
Who on earth is this person?

250
00:14:22,470 --> 00:14:23,260
Oh no.

251
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:26,460
I saw Snow-Tipped Jade
mentioned in a secret report,

252
00:14:26,930 --> 00:14:29,380
and I accidentally let it slip!

253
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:36,510
So even Xibao Pavilion
doesn't have such fine tea.

254
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:39,870
They say Xibao Pavilion
has countless treasures,

255
00:14:40,130 --> 00:14:42,390
but it seems that's an exaggeration.

256
00:14:43,740 --> 00:14:45,400
It's not that we don't have it,

257
00:14:45,570 --> 00:14:48,320
but even if Deputy Chief
wants to drink it,

258
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:50,410
he still needs Chief's approval.

259
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,810
What do you mean by that?

260
00:14:54,270 --> 00:14:55,860
I've met countless people,

261
00:14:55,890 --> 00:14:57,970
but just from the Snow-Tipped Jade,

262
00:14:58,120 --> 00:15:00,050
I wouldn't dare make assumptions.

263
00:15:00,730 --> 00:15:02,450
After all, Xibao Pavilion

264
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:05,490
often gets troublemakers.

265
00:15:06,070 --> 00:15:07,080
However,

266
00:15:07,110 --> 00:15:09,450
that jade belt at your waist

267
00:15:09,740 --> 00:15:11,640
was specially made by Xibao Pavilion.

268
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:13,190
Only two sets were made,

269
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:14,420
one for Chief,

270
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:16,060
and one for Deputy Chief.

271
00:15:16,420 --> 00:15:17,240
Deputy Chief,

272
00:15:17,570 --> 00:15:18,910
you came down from the mountain
without permission.

273
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:20,110
Does the Master know?

274
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,840
Ms. Li, please hush!

275
00:15:24,150 --> 00:15:26,090
Of course my brother doesn't know.

276
